---
import Layout from "@/layouts/main.astro"
import SiteHeader from "@/components/site-header"
import SiteFooter from "@/components/site-footer.astro"
---

<Layout
  title="AI во Veridex ERP"
  description="ERP без AI е само скапа табела. Veridex е ERP со AI — автоматско читање на фактури, анализа на профитабилност и детекција на аномалии."
>
  <SiteHeader client:load currentPath="/ai" />

  <main class="pt-24">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 via-transparent to-[oklch(0.48_0.22_275_/_0.05)]"></div>
      <div class="grid-pattern pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-30"></div>
      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-amber-600">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09ZM18.259 8.715 18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455 2.456L21.75 6l-1.036.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455 2.456ZM16.894 20.567 16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423 1.423Z" />
            </svg>
            Вештачка интелигенција
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
            ERP без AI е само
            <span class="text-gradient"> скапа табела</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Додека другите системи чекаат вие да внесувате, пребарувате и
            анализирате &mdash; Veridex го прави тоа наместо вас. Веќе денес,
            со уште повеќе утре.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why AI in ERP -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest text-primary uppercase">Зошто AI во ERP?</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">
          90% од времето во ERP е рачна работа
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          <p>
            Внесувате податоци, пребарувате информации, правите извештаи.
            ERP без AI само ги дигитализира фиоките &mdash; не ви помага
            да работите побрзо.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-foreground">Конкуренцијата нуди дигитализација.
            Ние нудиме интелигенција.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Active: AI Invoice Import -->
    <section class="bg-muted/30 py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6">
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest text-green-600 uppercase">Достапно денес</p>

        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border-2 border-green-200 bg-white p-8 md:p-12">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-500/10">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-amber-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09ZM18.259 8.715 18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455 2.456L21.75 6l-1.036.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455 2.456ZM16.894 20.567 16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423 1.423Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold md:text-3xl">AI увоз на фактури</h3>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-green-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold text-green-700 uppercase">Активно</span>
          </div>

          <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Повлечете PDF фактура во системот. AI го чита документот, ги
            извлекува сите ставки, износи, датуми и добавувачи &mdash; и
            автоматски ги пополнува. Вие само кликнете &bdquo;Зачувај&ldquo;.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-50 p-6">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-red-600">Пред:</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-2xl font-extrabold text-red-600">15-30 мин</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-red-500">рачно внесување по фактура</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-green-50 p-6">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-green-700">Со AI:</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-2xl font-extrabold text-green-700">10 секунди</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-green-600">нула грешки</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Coming soon -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6">
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest text-amber-600 uppercase">Во развој</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">
          Што доаѓа наскоро
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-muted-foreground">
          AI увозот на фактури е само почеток. Еве што градиме.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
          <!-- Profitability analysis -->
          <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 bg-white p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-500/5">
            <div class="mb-2 flex items-center justify-between">
              <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-amber-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09Z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-amber-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-amber-700 uppercase">Наскоро</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold">AI анализа на профитабилност</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
              Системот автоматски ја пресметува маржата по тура &mdash; приходи
              vs трошоци (гориво, возач, патарини, сервиси). Добивате
              известување: &bdquo;Тура TU-0045 имаше маржа 12%, под просекот
              од 18%. Главен причинител: гориво +34%.&ldquo;
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Anomaly detection -->
          <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 bg-white p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-500/5">
            <div class="mb-2 flex items-center justify-between">
              <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-amber-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09Z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-amber-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-amber-700 uppercase">Наскоро</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold">Детекција на аномалии</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
              AI ги следи вашите трошоци и ве предупредува кога нешто
              отстапува: трошок 3x повисок од просекот за тоа возило,
              невообичаено скап сервис, фактура од непознат добавувач.
              Проблемите ги гледате пред да станат загуби.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Natural language search -->
          <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 bg-white p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-500/5">
            <div class="mb-2 flex items-center justify-between">
              <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-amber-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09Z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-amber-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-amber-700 uppercase">Наскоро</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold">Пребарување на македонски</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
              Наместо да кликате низ филтри, напишете: &bdquo;покажи ми ги
              сите возила со трошок над 0.5 EUR/KM минатиот месец&ldquo; &mdash;
              и системот ви го дава одговорот. Како да прашувате колега кој
              знае сè.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="bg-muted/30 py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">
          Видете го AI
          <span class="text-gradient"> во акција</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg text-muted-foreground">
          Закажете демо и видете како AI чита фактури за 10 секунди.
          Сите модули + AI вклучени. 50 EUR / корисник / месец. Без договор.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center sm:gap-6">
          <a href="/kontakt">
            <button class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-[oklch(0.48_0.22_275)] px-10 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white shadow-2xl shadow-primary/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105">
              <span class="relative z-10">Закажи демо</span>
              <div class="animate-shimmer absolute inset-0 -z-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent"></div>
            </button>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/documents/veridex-ai.pdf"
            download
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base font-medium text-muted-foreground transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-primary"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 16.5v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 5.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 21 18.75V16.5M16.5 12 12 16.5m0 0L7.5 12m4.5 4.5V3" />
            </svg>
            Преземи AI документ
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <SiteFooter />
</Layout>
